Mr. GEORGE LOCKHART, the next Provost‚ was distinguished for his learning and his writings on Dialectics and Philosophy. He was a native of Ayr, and completed his education at the University of Paris; where for several years he was Professor of Natural Philosophy in the College of Montacute.
